{"title":"关于书","authors":["吴景慧"],"dates":[{"year":1995,"month":1,"day":16}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吴景慧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在书里滚大之后"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再重新拿起书时，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才掂出这书的分量"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"书摆在面前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也就出现了一条"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以文字为材料铺成的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跨越历史和现代文明之路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而铺路的人们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是以自己的心血"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和情感为代价"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以打破时空的伟力"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在书中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"塑造自己"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}